name: Andi Mack
overview: Andi is contemplative and artistic and sheltered by overprotective parents. But on the eve of her 13th birthday, Andi's free-spirited older sister Bex returns home with a revelation that changes everything and sends Andi on an uncharted course of self-discovery.

episodes.overview: Andi's world turns upside down when her older sister, Bex, returns home on her 13th birthday and reveals a family secret.

episodes.name: Outside the Box
episodes.overview: Andi decides to keep the news about Bex from her friends.

episodes.name: Shhh!
episodes.overview: Andi gets in trouble for the first time at school.

episodes.name: Dancing in the Dark
episodes.overview: Bex throws Andi a house party!

episodes.name: It's Not About You
episodes.overview: Andi's upset when Buffy and Bex spend time together.

episodes.name: She Said, She Said
episodes.overview: Andi tells Jonah about seeing Amber with another guy.

episodes.name: Dad Influence
episodes.overview: Bex and Cyrus have news for Andi.

episodes.name: Terms of Embarrassment
episodes.overview: Andi must adjust to Bowie being in her life full time.

episodes.name: She's Turning Into You
episodes.overview: Jonah asks Andi to help him pick out a gift for Amber.

episodes.name: Home Away From Home
episodes.overview: Andi and Bex adjust to their new living arrangement.

episodes.name: Were We Ever?
episodes.overview: Bex helps Andi stand up against the new dress code.

episodes.name: Best Surprise Ever
episodes.overview: Amber fails to defend Jonah when her friends mock him.

episodes.name: Hey, Who Wants Pizza?
episodes.overview: Andi encourages Bowie to plan a future with Bex; Cyrus introduces his girlfriend, Iris, to Andi and Buffy; Jonah invites Andi to the Space Otters' party.

episodes.name: Chinese New Year
episodes.overview: Andi invites Jonah to her Chinese New Year celebration, which gets awkward when Celia’s sister Aunt Mei visits. Buffy signs up for the boys’ basketball team tryouts.

episodes.name: Friends Like These
episodes.overview: Andi tries to convince her friends to find a new hangout spot to avoid Amber at The Spoon. Buffy tries out for the boys’ basketball team.

episodes.name: Mama
episodes.overview: Andi learns more about her past on the anniversary of the day Bex left home. Jonah attempts to teach Cyrus how to skateboard.

episodes.name: The Snorpion
episodes.overview: Andi invites Amber over for a sleepover. Buffy is frustrated when the basketball team captain TJ excludes her from gameplay.

episodes.name: I Wanna Hold Your Wristband
episodes.overview: Andi takes a stand when students are divided into two groups, and one group receives preferential treatment at her school. Andi also learns AndiShack is in jeopardy.

episodes.name: Head Over Heels
episodes.overview: Andi and Jonah go on a double date with Buffy and Marty to an arcade; meanwhile, Cyrus decides to shoot a movie with Bex's encouragement.

episodes.name: There's a Mack in the Shack
episodes.overview: When Andi and Celia spend more time together, Bex feels jealous; Buffy agrees to tutor TJ if he agrees to pass her the ball on the court.

episodes.name: You're the One That I Want
episodes.overview: Andi questions her relationship with Jonah; after a discouraging talk with Amber, Andi enlists Buffy and Cyrus to investigate.

episodes.name: A Good Hair Day
episodes.overview: Andi and Bex plan a surprise party for Bowie's birthday; Jonah joins Andi, Cyrus and Buffy on their annual trip to the Renaissance Faire.

episodes.name: Miniature Gulf
episodes.overview: Andi and Bex discover that Bowie may be seeing someone; Cyrus is selected to make a video for the school, but realizes he may be better behind the camera.

episodes.name: We Were Never
episodes.overview: Andi is left confused when Jonah stops wearing the bracelet and tells her he doesn’t like labels. At her basketball game, Buffy finally gets what she has been hoping for.

episodes.name: Cyrus' Bash-Mitzvah!
episodes.overview: After much preparation and planning, Cyrus’ Bar Mitzvah festivities commence. Andi and her friends and family all join him in the celebration, which is full of landmark events for more than just Cyrus.

episodes.name: Better to Have Wuvved and Wost
episodes.overview: Jonah tries to express his feelings for Andi through gifts, which proves not to be his forte. Buffy reveals she has to move, and Andi devises a plan for her to stay.

episodes.name: Perfect Day 2.0
episodes.overview: With a week to go until Buffy moves, Andi seeks to recreate the "perfect" day that she, Buffy and Cyrus experienced years ago, which included their first alpine slide.

episodes.name: Truth or Truth
episodes.overview: When the power goes out in Shadyside, a day of fun and games shed light on unexpected revelations.

episodes.name: A Walker to Remember
episodes.overview: Andi and Walker realize how much they have in common when they spend the day together. Buffy steps up to lead the team in T.J.'s place when he is side-lined.

episodes.name: Crime Scene: AndiShack!
episodes.overview: A special craft project goes missing when Andi agrees to let Miranda’s daughter spend the day at AndiShack. Jonah confides in Buffy and Cyrus.

episodes.name: Andi’s Choice
episodes.overview: Jonah finds a way to tell Andi how much he truly likes being around her; Walker continues to make a positive impression on Andi and her friends.

episodes.name: For the Last Time
episodes.overview: Andi, Cyrus and Jonah put together a farewell gift for Buffy before her last day in Shadyside.

episodes.name: Buffy in a Bottle
episodes.overview: Andi and Cyrus miss Buffy and can't reach her after her move; Andi receives a handmade gift from Walker that upsets Jonah.

episodes.name: Keep a Lid on It
episodes.overview: Ham reveals surprising news to Andi and Bex. Jonah tries out for a regional league Ultimate team.

episodes.name: Bought, Lost Or Stolen
episodes.overview: Andi runs into Walker at an art fair, and he meets Jonah for the first time. Bowie’s relationship with Miranda hits a snag.

episodes.name: We’re On Cloud Ten
episodes.overview: Andi and Jonah go on their first date where she learns some sad news. Bex and Celia prepare for the grand opening of their business.

episodes.name: The Cake That Takes The Cake
episodes.overview: Andi and Bex plan a special dinner for Bowie, but unexpected company drops in to crash the party.

episodes.name: The Boys Are Back
episodes.overview: Andi anxiously awaits Jonah’s return from summer camp; Andi is surprised to learn who Buffy likes; Bex gives Celia a makeover.

episodes.name: Howling at the Moon Festival
episodes.overview: Friends and family gather to celebrate the Harvest Moon Festival, but Jonah's mishap may spoil the evening; Celia attempts to one-up her sister, Mei, by announcing a special event; Andi and Jonah have a heart-to-heart talk about their relationship.

episodes.name: It's a Dilemna
episodes.overview: Andi's plans for a group outing with Buffy, Cyrus and Jonah are interrupted by Walker; Bowie's new guitar student proves to be a challenge; Cyrus seeks an alternative to P.E. and ends up in a dance class.

episodes.name: Hole in the Wall
episodes.overview: Andi is embarrassed when Jonah performs a song about her; Bowie decides to renovate Bex and Andi's apartment to make it big enough for their whole family to live in; Buffy conducts her first girls' basketball team tryouts.

episodes.name: That Syncing Feeling
episodes.overview: Feeling left out by her friends, Andi spends time with Amber; Andi and Celia pick out Bex's wedding cake; Bowie helps a guitar student break some bad news.

episodes.name: Cookie Monster
episodes.overview: Andi, Bowie and Bex are surprised by an impromptu visit by Bowie's mother; while hanging out with T.J.'s friends, Cyrus faces a dangerous situation; Buffy and Jonah learn a secret about their school principal.

episodes.name: The New Girls
episodes.overview: Andi questions her friendship with Buffy; Cyrus comes clean with his friends.

episodes.name: I Got Your Number
episodes.overview: Andi gets in over her head when she attends a high school party with Amber, causing Bowie's plans for a romantic outing with Bex to go awry; Cyrus tries to mend a longtime rift between Jonah and T.J.

episodes.name: Secret Society
episodes.overview: Invitations from a secret society at school cause tension between Andi and her friends; Bex and Celia search for the perfect wedding dress.

episodes.name: The Quacks
episodes.overview: Andi lends a hand when Buffy's coaching skills are tested at the school's first girls' basketball game; Amber helps Cyrus create a dance routine; Libby is disappointed that Jonah hasn't learned sign language.

episodes.name: One in a Minyan
episodes.overview: Andi, Buffy and Jonah support Cyrus as he sits shiva for his grandmother; Bowie's homemade kugel dish creates a scandal.

episodes.name: The Ex Factor
episodes.overview: Andi, Buffy and Cyrus worry about Jonah's unusual behavior; Miranda tries to cause problems for Bowie and Bex.

episodes.name: Mount Rushmore or Less
episodes.overview: Andi attempts to enlist her friends in an epic group costume; Amber continues to vie for Jonah's attention; Bex makes a confession to Andi.

episodes.name: Hammer Time
episodes.overview: Andi releases her frustrations about Bex and Bowie’s canceled wedding; Cyrus invites Jonah to a backyard campout; Buffy competes in a marathon with Marty.

episodes.name: Unloading Zone
episodes.overview: Andi, Buffy, Jonah and Cyrus take a stand against a wasteful clothing company; Cyrus is disappointed by T.J.’s new friendship; Celia refuses to forgive Bex.

episodes.name: One Girl's Trash
episodes.overview: Andi creates an art project to combat stereotypes; Bowie reveals his true feelings about the wedding; Jonah and Amber are not on the same page with their relationship.

episodes.name: Arts and Inhumanities
episodes.overview: Andi learns about a life-changing opportunity; Cyrus counsels Amber about her relationship with Jonah; Buffy has an awkward meeting with Marty’s ex.

episodes.name: Something to Talk A-boot
episodes.overview: Andi makes a big decision about her future; T.J.’s act of kindness toward Buffy lands him in trouble; Amber asks Jonah for some space.

episodes.name: A Moving Day
episodes.overview: Andi and her family take a road trip. While helping Jonah move, Buffy and Cyrus are surprised to learn the identity of his famous mom.

episodes.name: We Were Here
episodes.overview: When Celia leaves town, Andi and Bex throw another party; Buffy and Cyrus share relationship woes; Andi shares a secret.
